---
title: Homemade Chorizo & Peri Peri Pizza with Fresh Dough & Radish Salad
description: Who needs takeaway when homemade can taste this good? Introducing our new favourite pizza topping combo - peri peri sauce takes the place of your usual tomato base, with chorizo, onion and shredded cheese sprinkled liberally over the top. Add a sweet pear salad for a burst of freshness and you’re on to a winner!

*We’ve replaced the radish in this recipe with pear due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
